Usage: vcpe status [flags]

Reports reconcile metrics, active IPAM leases, and recent operation history. With --name, shows the desired state snapshot for that deployment.

Optional flags:
  --name <deployment>     Filter output to a specific deployment
  --state-root <path>     Override the default state root directory
  --json                  Emit structured JSON with metrics, timeline, desired, planned, observed, and runtimeInitDiagnostics keys

Examples:
  vcpe status
  vcpe status --name bng-7
  vcpe status --json
